Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.70,0:00:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說十五日盂蘭盆節當日\N(※盂蘭盆節為日本的清明節)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.50,0:00:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不能出海捕魚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.00,0:00:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是某個港口的傳統
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.47,0:00:12.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,儘管如此
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.47,0:00:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾名不信這項傳統的年輕漁夫
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.61,0:00:16.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將船駛向大海
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.48,0:00:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當他們到了海中央
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.95,0:00:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頃刻間天空烏雲密佈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.89,0:00:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四周盡是詭譎的濃霧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.00,0:00:36.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂~那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.20,0:00:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此時前方出現了一艘鬼船
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.04,0:00:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是由在暴風雨的海上\N喪生的亡魂所操縱的船
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.11,0:00:50.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼船上的亡魂們\N用可怕的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.45,0:00:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對年輕的漁夫們說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.52,0:00:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把長柄杓給我…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.06,0:01:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂的長柄杓\N即是握柄很長的杓子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.96,0:01:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漁夫們害怕如果不照他們的話做
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.00,0:01:11.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將帶來可怕的後果
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.17,0:01:12.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此就把長柄杓交給那些亡魂…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.83,0:01:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我~我知道之後怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.91,0:01:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後亡魂用那些杓子汲取海水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.67,0:01:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把漁船弄沉對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.41,0:01:22.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.61,0:01:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了！就是那麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.58,0:01:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從此以後漁夫出海\N都會準備無底的杓子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.89,0:01:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是幻映齋大人\N真是博學多聞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.69,0:01:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.79,0:01:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說我們大家互不相識
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.20,0:01:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但至少有緣一同搭船旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.36,0:01:44.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這時候說這些話可能有些魯莽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.97,0:01:48.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但要不要藉此機會\N大家來做個自我介紹呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.60,0:01:50.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就由小的先開始好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.87,0:01:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敝人三國屋多門
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.48,0:01:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這艘船過去曾是\N御朱印船的空栗鼠丸號
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.92,0:02:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敝人也算是個小小商人啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.88,0:02:06.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…在下柳幻映齋
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.96,0:02:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如您所見乃修行之人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.96,0:02:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一面驅除\N不該存在於世上的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.29,0:02:15.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一面雲遊四海\N幹嘛要跟歐吉桑們自我介紹啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.20,0:02:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊~那這位小姑娘呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.47,0:02:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個我叫加世
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.60,0:02:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前在坂井家幫傭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.17,0:02:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊~就是那個\N有貓妖出現的坂井家？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.01,0:02:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦~這麼有名啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.75,0:02:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的！沒錯！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.55,0:02:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此現在打算到江戶\N另找幫傭的工作
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.85,0:02:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…那邊那位武士大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.96,0:02:43.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知可否請教您的大名？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.93,0:02:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐佐木兵衛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.26,0:02:50.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹽治藩藩士
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.17,0:02:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝賜教
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.67,0:02:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樓下的兩位呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.50,0:02:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位是五代寺的源慧師父
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.84,0:03:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下是負責服侍師父的菖源
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.85,0:03:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到能與\N這位聲名遠播的高僧同行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.92,0:03:13.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…海跟和尚\N(註：“和尚”日文發音即“坊主”)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.06,0:03:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.16,0:03:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(海坊主)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.89,0:03:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍色的月光照着你徘徊的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.60,0:03:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想說的話卻說不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.57,0:04:01.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日子令人如此不耐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.50,0:04:06.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猶記那虛偽的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.04,0:04:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘卻那溫暖的淚水
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.48,0:04:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那雙失了魂的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.18,0:04:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,映照着什麼樣的風景？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.26,0:04:24.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虛幻的下弦月隱臟在雲間
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.96,0:04:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗如今正慢慢浮現
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.06,0:04:28.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,述說着真相
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.03,0:04:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擁抱着孤獨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.87,0:04:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚是否又將對月長嘆…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.84,0:04:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(序之章第一夜)
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.31,0:04:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過這艘船還真奇怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.18,0:04:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船上竟然有魚池
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.39,0:04:56.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈這我就要跟您詳細解釋了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.92,0:04:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是特別設計的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.19,0:05:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請您再仔細看看
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.03,0:05:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇~好大的金魚！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.60,0:05:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.94,0:05:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼特別的水池\N可說是絕無僅有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.01,0:05:17.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡面到底有幾隻啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.21,0:05:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.08,0:05:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？好像還有一位客人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.78,0:05:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.95,0:05:26.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是那個賣藥的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.45,0:05:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個人\N平定坂井家的貓妖事件的！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.39,0:05:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有風…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.46,0:05:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是咒術師嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.60,0:05:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是個…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.90,0:05:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普通的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.30,0:05:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賣藥郎喲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.91,0:05:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果風勢不錯的話
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.55,0:05:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概四五天內就能抵達江戶了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.91,0:05:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧！五浪丸？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.52,0:05:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.25,0:05:59.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚好像沒有星星啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.55,0:06:02.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有星星有什麼關係？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.39,0:06:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個羅盤會一直指向北方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.66,0:06:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此只要朝着鬼門的方向前進
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.20,0:06:10.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定能抵達江戶的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.63,0:06:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼門的方向…嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.31,0:06:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果又有妖怪出現的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.84,0:06:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賣藥的會再拿出退魔劍吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.38,0:06:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.61,0:06:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還問我為什麼，因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.52,0:06:32.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪是不得存在於世上之物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.12,0:06:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其數量可是數也數不清
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.26,0:06:40.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要將他們全部斬除\N會沒完沒了的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.03,0:06:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,數也數不清的是\N神明大人的數量吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.43,0:06:46.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.83,0:06:50.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是物怪不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.79,0:07:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這位先生…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.96,0:07:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可否拔出那把退魔劍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.46,0:07:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我看看呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.46,0:07:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.17,0:07:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要拔出退魔劍是有條件的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.17,0:07:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須找出物怪的\N“形”、“真”、“理”
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.51,0:07:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個愛裝模作樣的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.84,0:07:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想必也沒多大的靈力
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.98,0:07:32.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相較之下我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.38,0:07:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(當晚)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.08,0:09:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,風…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.78,0:09:12.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.22,0:09:23.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(第二晚)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.07,0:09:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.17,0:09:40.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛？大家都在這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.41,0:09:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還想說你們跑哪兒去了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.18,0:09:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…發生了什麼事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.08,0:09:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…這該怎麼說呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.29,0:09:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早已是早晨的時間
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.22,0:09:55.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻遲遲未見太陽出現
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.12,0:10:00.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但天還是有些亮光
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.83,0:10:04.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,源慧師父天氣有些冷\N已經早上了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.07,0:10:08.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請回屋裡去吧\N這個時間早該看到石廊崎了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.90,0:10:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？可是什麼都沒看到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.82,0:10:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.02,0:10:26.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這兒是新島
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.96,0:10:32.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後這裡是野島崎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.56,0:10:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.93,0:10:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點也沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.66,0:10:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.17,0:10:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新島、野島崎\N跟這附近的南蠻島嶼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.50,0:10:43.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這三點連接起來的海域
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.97,0:10:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是傳說中被稱為“龍三角”的海域
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.98,0:10:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,龍…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.21,0:10:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三角？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.22,0:10:56.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.42,0:10:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說任何進入這片海域的船隻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.22,0:11:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都會被不屬於\N這世上的妖怪襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.12,0:11:07.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再也無法回到陸地上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.20,0:11:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,意思是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.93,0:11:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.44,0:11:17.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪之海
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.67,0:11:20.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖…妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.71,0:11:23.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼可能！五浪丸！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.75,0:11:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請看
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.91,0:11:31.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這指針\N還是一直指着鬼門的方向啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.82,0:11:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯確實如此
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.23,0:11:47.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這根鐵棒有磁性
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.17,0:11:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要將它…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.31,0:11:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擺在羅盤附近
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.21,0:11:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能隨意操縱方位\N真是奇怪的妖術
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.65,0:12:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究…究竟是誰幹這種事的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.48,0:12:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這表示…那個人就在我們之中囉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.03,0:12:17.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是太鼓
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.50,0:12:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.17,0:12:20.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是那個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.57,0:12:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被稱為虛空太鼓的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.90,0:12:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖、妖怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.64,0:12:29.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯在海上聽到的太鼓聲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.88,0:12:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這並不會對人造成危害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.31,0:12:35.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真遺憾啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.62,0:12:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是鬼船出現的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.89,0:12:42.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下馬上就讓它升天成佛！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.42,0:13:10.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.93,0:13:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.38,0:13:43.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子我們被困住了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.85,0:13:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.65,0:13:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,源慧師父
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.99,0:13:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這應該是某人做的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.39,0:13:52.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要動搖菖源
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.63,0:13:56.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪最容易依附在\N軟弱害怕的人身上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.23,0:13:57.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是的！可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.20,0:14:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是龍三角妖怪之海
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.50,0:14:03.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.10,0:14:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加世小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.84,0:14:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.71,0:14:07.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是天秤
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.24,0:14:08.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,耶？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.28,0:14:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天秤？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.75,0:14:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要稱什麼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.42,0:14:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是用來稱重的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.48,0:14:18.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是用來測量距離的天秤
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.75,0:14:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距離？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.75,0:14:21.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼和什麼的距離？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.29,0:14:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,測不存在於這世上的東西喲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.90,0:14:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.71,0:14:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這就是傳說中的鬼船嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.11,0:14:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從沒聽說它這麼大
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.11,0:14:49.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是要將之斬除
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.78,0:14:52.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是擺在江戶當展覽品
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.69,0:14:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙看起來還真適合呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.26,0:14:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何不用你的退魔劍斬除呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.46,0:15:04.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想見識一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.43,0:15:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不是說過了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.50,0:15:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要“形”，“真”，“理”\N三個條件啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.91,0:15:13.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個“形”\N好像已經可以看到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.61,0:15:14.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.18,0:15:20.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.69,0:15:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出現了過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.36,0:15:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賣藥的！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.53,0:15:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船的…亡魂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.10,0:15:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退魔劍沒有動靜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.87,0:15:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位冷靜點準備好杓子！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.67,0:15:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種東西…派不上用場吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.27,0:15:47.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.98,0:15:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這妖怪不是那麼好對付的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.11,0:15:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,況且他也沒說要杓子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.58,0:15:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那些亡魂有什麼要求？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.62,0:16:01.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它們說…加入我們
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.16,0:16:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不想變成那副德性啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.62,0:16:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船主
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.73,0:16:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點去把灶裡的灰拿過來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.76,0:16:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,灰嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.00,0:16:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯！快點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.33,0:16:14.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！五浪丸~
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.80,0:16:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也去幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.81,0:16:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不撒鹽而是撒灰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.14,0:16:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這問題問的好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.44,0:16:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鹽的話海裡多的是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.78,0:16:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那對鬼船是沒用的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.22,0:16:32.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就沒問題了\N是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.56,0:16:47.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行~根本沒用~
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.50,0:16:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疑？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.87,0:16:52.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船主\N你怎麼處理綁木柴的繩索？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.11,0:16:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的！就跟木柴一起燒了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.78,0:16:56.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.98,0:17:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果夾雜木柴以外的灰燼…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.51,0:17:03.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會失去驅逐亡魂的效果
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.25,0:17:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.92,0:17:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.09,0:17:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.35,0:17:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐着等待
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.22,0:17:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有違武士道的精神
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.06,0:17:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙並沒有生命
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.53,0:17:20.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺人用的工具是起不了作用的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.70,0:17:24.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.52,0:17:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛…飛起來了~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.62,0:17:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的船啊~\N好…好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.79,0:17:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賣藥的請您想想辦法啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.33,0:17:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賣藥的確是我的職業
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.00,0:17:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼還這麼悠哉！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.47,0:17:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些藥對妖怪應該更沒用吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.81,0:18:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了幻映齋大人是個修行者吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.04,0:18:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.05,0:18:06.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問您會破邪的咒術嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.98,0:18:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那當然
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.18,0:18:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就先拜託您了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.05,0:18:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,調製藥物需要花點時間…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.73,0:18:27.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪透過黑暗來到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.70,0:18:32.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這群妖怪已經強到\N哇…這下完蛋了~
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.57,0:18:35.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可掩蓋太陽的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.31,0:18:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.04,0:18:40.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們只能乖乖被抓嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.75,0:18:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光明並非只存在於天空之中
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.55,0:18:49.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,張開眼睛可是會瞎掉的喲！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.55,0:19:20.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼船消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.75,0:19:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你不是普通的賣藥郎呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.42,0:19:25.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺有兩把刷子的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.53,0:19:28.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就說這個人很厲害的喲~
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.13,0:19:31.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,源慧師父我們得救了對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.40,0:19:35.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那那是什麼聲音啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.67,0:19:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是鎖鏈的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.01,0:19:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點也沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.07,0:19:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡可是妖怪之海呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.61,0:19:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們怎麼會到這種地方啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.41,0:19:48.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯到底是誰在羅盤動手腳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.52,0:19:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這艘船引到這裡來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.32,0:19:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能確定是我們之中的某人幹的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.66,0:19:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可別算在下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.72,0:19:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是幻映齋先生不是說過
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.29,0:20:02.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想打敗妖怪以獲取名聲嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.56,0:20:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至於三國屋大人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.23,0:20:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要更多\N像那些大金魚的珍禽異獸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.07,0:20:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐佐木大人非常想看那把退魔劍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.24,0:20:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可以說\N其實你很想要那把劍吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.08,0:20:21.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼懷疑是妳的事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.72,0:20:23.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不是我做的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.22,0:20:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天晚上\N菖源先生在途中就不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.19,0:20:30.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那那是因為我暈船
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.02,0:20:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以到甲板上吹風
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.59,0:20:36.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了賣藥的之外
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.16,0:20:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的人都有嫌疑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.93,0:20:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來會出現什麼妖怪呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.87,0:20:50.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了對了火藥已經全用掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.71,0:20:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來\N就不能再用剛剛那個方法了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.48,0:21:01.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這麼開心難道…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.09,0:21:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該不會…連賣藥的也…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.89,0:21:10.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(待續)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.03,0:21:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當你不在身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.60,0:21:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就無法笑得開懷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.41,0:21:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這平凡的街道上
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.01,0:21:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是如此地被你吸引
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.38,0:21:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若能將那些無可取代的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.99,0:21:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好珍惜並活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.93,0:21:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也別無所求
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.41,0:22:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盛開在那片天空下的夏之花
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.38,0:22:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨風緩緩飄落
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.75,0:22:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星光落在早已看不見的夜空
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.26,0:22:24.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那段日子將是我此生無可比喻的珍愛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.22,0:22:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人乃好變之物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.28,0:22:39.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時乃變動之物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.52,0:22:41.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海乃莫測之物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.06,0:22:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的地相同的眾人搭船同行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.59,0:22:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一望無際的海洋
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.26,0:22:49.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浪的顏色高度
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.70,0:22:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都與往常不同
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.73,0:22:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪物怪海坊主
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.64,0:23:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要人的心中有黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.24,0:23:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將有絡繹不絕之物造訪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.78,0:23:04.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但最可怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.85,0:23:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃是內心的誘惑之音！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.88,0:23:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(海坊主)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.64,0:23:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍色的月光照着你徘徊的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.45,0:23:49.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想說的話卻說不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.36,0:23:53.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日子令人如此不耐
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.19,0:23:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猶記那虛偽的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.80,0:24:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘卻那溫暖的淚水
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.04,0:24:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那雙失了魂的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.94,0:24:11.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,映照着什麼樣的風景？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.98,0:24:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虛幻的下弦月隱臟在雲間
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.62,0:24:18.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗如今正慢慢浮現
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.79,0:24:20.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,述說着真相
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.75,0:24:25.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擁抱着孤獨
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.63,0:24:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚是否又將對月長嘆…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.47,0:24:33.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(第二幕)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.75,0:24:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確是賣藥的\N鎮壓了坂井家的貓妖
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.95,0:24:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是坂井家後來也一蹶不振
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.92,0:24:57.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救的到底是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.69,0:25:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人到底是站在哪一邊的？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.06,0:25:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表情太可怕會嫁不出去的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.90,0:25:08.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要你管
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.74,0:25:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然問了你也不一定會說真話
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.14,0:25:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我還是要問
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.34,0:25:17.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是你在羅盤上動手腳的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.28,0:25:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.32,0:25:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算不在羅盤上動手腳
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.42,0:25:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一定會來到這片妖怪之海喲
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.59,0:25:35.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被誰帶來？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.47,0:25:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難不成這把劍是有生命的？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.50,0:25:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛…誰知道呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.17,0:25:45.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說賣藥的！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.17,0:25:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我承認你是個很厲害的人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.48,0:25:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是你這種裝模作樣的態度
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.51,0:25:53.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會讓人很火大喲
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.18,0:25:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這樣會不受女孩子歡迎的！
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.99,0:26:00.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.72,0:26:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你曾說過妖怪跟物怪不同對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.46,0:26:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我覺得根本就一樣啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.86,0:26:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為妖怪跟神明也是相同的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.13,0:26:15.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誠如人鳥獸存在的道理
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.24,0:26:19.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不該存於世上的妖怪\N也隨處可見
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.21,0:26:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪也是死去的人變成的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.44,0:26:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實有此一說
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.78,0:26:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方才的亡魂即屬此類
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.05,0:26:30.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不僅有這類型的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.85,0:26:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有附在物體或工具上面的類型
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.39,0:26:35.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,性質可是天差地遠喲
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.22,0:26:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是不管什麼原因
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.16,0:26:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類是無法理解妖怪的道理的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.03,0:26:42.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那物怪呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.53,0:26:45.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳知道物怪“モノノ怪”的“怪”\N所指何物嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.83,0:26:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是不知道才問啊
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.80,0:26:49.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“怪”指的是疾病喲
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.57,0:26:52.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而“モノノ”指的是炎神
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.51,0:26:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說來
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.67,0:26:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物怪就是造成人類生病的神囉
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.01,0:26:59.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怨懟悲傷憎恨
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.15,0:27:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當這些強烈的情感與妖怪結合後\N會發生什麼事呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.05,0:27:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將成為連咒術\N都無法對印的修羅之眾
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.06,0:27:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過那把退魔劍卻可將之斬除
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.26,0:27:13.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是若沒找出物怪的…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.06,0:27:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“形”“真”“理”這三個條件\N劍是拔不出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.43,0:27:22.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所謂的“真”與“理”是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.74,0:27:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“真”乃事情的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.44,0:27:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“理”乃心的樣貌
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.21,0:27:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦？原因與樣貌啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.88,0:27:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那這片大海不只有妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.68,0:27:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有物怪是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.14,0:27:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了那兩個和尚真靠不住
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.77,0:28:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是妖怪或是物怪
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.11,0:28:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我的咒術面前都將遁逃退散的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.65,0:28:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.55,0:28:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就來
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.95,0:28:13.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.62,0:28:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次…有點麻煩喲
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.10,0:28:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼有這麼多鬼火？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.44,0:28:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亮是件好事但還真詭異
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.81,0:28:38.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有什麼東西\N從橋上過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.62,0:28:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…妖怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.96,0:28:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該一刀就能解決
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.89,0:28:56.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊~果然是妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.00,0:28:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在空中飄來飄去的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.87,0:29:00.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是海座頭
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.73,0:29:02.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武士刀是對付不了他的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.34,0:29:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那該怎麼辦呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.08,0:29:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙會提出問題
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.81,0:29:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他會問是否覺得他的模樣很可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.65,0:29:15.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千萬不能回答可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.78,0:29:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要回答一點也不可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.18,0:29:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣他就會離開嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.19,0:29:24.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.42,0:29:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…喔~我想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.16,0:29:28.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要回答這趟旅程的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.13,0:29:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道將會發生何事
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.70,0:29:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才是最可怕的\N就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.47,0:29:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船上的人我要提問了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.01,0:29:42.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.31,0:29:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個一個回答
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.94,0:29:45.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不回答的人
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.91,0:29:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將成為海上的亡魂
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.25,0:29:52.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠遊蕩於這片海域之上
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.25,0:29:53.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好儘管問吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.42,0:29:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.29,0:29:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.53,0:30:09.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最害怕的事是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.74,0:30:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這…這趟旅程的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.47,0:30:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道將會發生何事…
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.64,0:30:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真正害怕的事是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.18,0:30:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其…其實我最害怕失去所有財產
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.02,0:30:27.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變成身無分文的窮光蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.22,0:30:57.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的寶貝南蠻金魚
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.02,0:31:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我砸了大錢甚至改造船身\N好不容易才把你們運上船的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.33,0:31:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最害怕的事是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.97,0:31:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這世上無所畏懼
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.81,0:31:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自這把九字兼定入手後
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.84,0:31:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已有百餘性命喪於此刀之下
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.61,0:31:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是個殺人魔啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.75,0:31:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是很想砍一次妖怪看看
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.72,0:31:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說那是不可能的了！
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.01,0:31:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐佐木兵衛
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.34,0:31:58.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我找你很久了…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.68,0:32:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兵衛大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.55,0:32:02.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這些亡魂
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.32,0:32:03.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我滾回地獄吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.22,0:32:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該下地獄的人是你\N佐佐木兵衛
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.69,0:32:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石…石井師父！
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.86,0:32:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺你的人不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.39,0:32:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這把兼定
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.46,0:32:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我要到江戶…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.30,0:32:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你快點成佛吧~
Dialogue: 0,0:32:39.89,0:32:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武士大人
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.39,0:32:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個武士說\N自已無所畏懼原來是騙人的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.86,0:32:48.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說過去所殺的人
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.90,0:32:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才是他一直害怕的東西呢
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.70,0:32:53.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是說謊會怎麼樣呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.83,0:32:56.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像那樣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.34,0:32:58.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,照目前的情況看來
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.30,0:33:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那妖怪早已看穿\N每個人心中的恐懼了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.08,0:33:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎~
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.11,0:33:06.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那說真話或謊話都一樣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.91,0:33:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底該怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.92,0:33:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是自已內心的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.89,0:33:15.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問別人也無濟於事
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.16,0:33:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來你說的麻煩是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.99,0:33:22.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人！
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.33,0:33:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳最害怕的事是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.90,0:33:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已…已經輪到我了？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.77,0:33:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在你最可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.71,0:33:36.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我最害怕的事是什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.24,0:33:37.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點回答！
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.58,0:33:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不要催我啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.61,0:33:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…我還沒談過轟轟烈烈的愛情
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.22,0:33:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,往後我一定會遇到\N非常快樂的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.19,0:33:50.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有幸福地結婚\N產下可愛的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.59,0:33:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是還沒體驗到人生的美好\N就這麼死掉
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.56,0:33:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是我最害怕的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.27,0:34:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要不要啦~
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.24,0:34:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還沒嫁人耶！
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.44,0:34:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不要在這時候生小孩呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.35,0:34:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.38,0:34:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海座頭讓妳看到的都是幻覺
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.55,0:34:51.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過是場惡夢而已
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.35,0:34:53.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加世小姐的“真”並沒有改變
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.19,0:34:56.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賣藥的…
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.86,0:35:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來輪到在下了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.13,0:35:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最害怕的事是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.23,0:35:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在…在下最害怕的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.77,0:35:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饅…饅頭
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.17,0:35:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下最怕饅頭
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.21,0:35:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在講冷笑話嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.88,0:35:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.62,0:35:33.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可口的酒蒸…
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.04,0:35:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海座頭究竟讓他看到什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.51,0:35:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可一點都不敢想像
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.01,0:35:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了剩下三個人
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.81,0:35:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰要先回答海座頭的問題呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.08,0:36:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來回答
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.05,0:36:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最害怕的事是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.83,0:36:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最害怕的
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.56,0:36:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這世上毫無“形”“真”“理”
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.40,0:36:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而世界只是這麼存在着
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.04,0:36:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.84,0:36:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賣藥的…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.11,0:37:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖怪聚集的物怪之海
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.25,0:37:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道\N你讓這艘船航向此處的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.29,0:37:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.49,0:37:18.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最害怕的事…是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.30,0:37:22.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我最害怕的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.47,0:37:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我最害怕的是源慧師父
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.04,0:37:32.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,源慧師父是非常了不起的師父
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.48,0:37:36.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在前往江戶的旅程中
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.15,0:37:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他變得很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.72,0:37:40.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.22,0:37:44.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天本來還一直在誦經的…
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.80,0:37:55.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菖源
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.47,0:37:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的源慧師父
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.64,0:38:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這趟漫長的船旅讓你暈船了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.17,0:38:02.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.51,0:38:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果暈船就去吹吹海風吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.58,0:38:07.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.28,0:38:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果暈船就去吹吹海風吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.15,0:38:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.52,0:38:13.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.99,0:38:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我不想相信這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.49,0:38:18.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我到了甲板上之後
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.83,0:38:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻看見源慧師父…
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.13,0:38:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在羅盤上動手腳！
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.86,0:38:52.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼要這麼做？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.86,0:38:55.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我並不想連累大家
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.43,0:38:58.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不管我怎麼拜託
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.50,0:39:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都沒有人願意帶我到龍之三角
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.07,0:39:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您在發抖呢
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.44,0:39:12.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓您不惜這麼害怕\N也要到這裡的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.35,0:39:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海座頭提問吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.18,0:39:22.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最害怕的事是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.72,0:39:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來你是在等這一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.59,0:39:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這五十年來我一直想着這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.23,0:39:33.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這件讓我恐懼不已的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.63,0:39:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在這片大海之中
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.81,0:39:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它一直在這片海域漂流
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.74,0:39:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到把這片海\N變成妖怪聚集的鬼海
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.95,0:39:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那到底是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.72,0:39:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.66,0:40:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,創造出妖怪之海的罪魁禍首
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.09,0:40:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.73,0:40:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五十年前\N舍妹所搭乘的獨木舟
Dialogue: 0,0:40:35.73,0:40:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海座頭消失了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.56,0:40:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼是“獨木舟”啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.87,0:40:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是將大樹挖空做成的船
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.34,0:40:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中空的船怎麼可能出得了海
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.61,0:40:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯就是出不了海
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.34,0:40:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它的用意就是在此
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.78,0:40:54.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.91,0:40:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,源慧師父的妹妹\N為什麼要搭那種船呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.12,0:41:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊~是鎖鏈的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.46,0:41:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是獨木舟的鎖鏈的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.50,0:41:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這艘船也是幻覺嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.30,0:41:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是幻覺我也看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.11,0:41:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,源慧師父
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.54,0:41:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五十年前到底發生了什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.51,0:42:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令妹\N為何要搭上這艘船呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.45,0:42:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這艘小船
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.05,0:42:07.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓這片海變成這樣的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.53,0:42:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼聲音？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.50,0:42:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是從裡面傳出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.30,0:42:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是人有人在裡面！
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.21,0:42:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從五十年前就一直在裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.54,0:42:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.34,0:42:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊我受不了了！
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.78,0:42:38.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我受夠這些可怕的事了！
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.88,0:42:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想知道物怪的“真”與“理”
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.26,0:42:49.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請仔細道來吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.90,0:42:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請妳原諒我吧！阿庸
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.70,0:42:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這五十年來我無時無刻都想着妳
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.71,0:43:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是代替我坐進這艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.08,0:43:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,漂向龍三角的妳
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.91,0:43:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然一直懷着
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.98,0:43:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,足以把這片海化為\N妖怪之海的怨恨嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.76,0:43:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會變成這樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.70,0:43:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物怪的“形”
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.57,0:43:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現身吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:43:39.35,0:43:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(待續)
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.52,0:43:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當你不在身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.15,0:43:51.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就無法笑得開懷
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.89,0:43:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這平凡的街道上
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.39,0:44:01.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是如此地被你吸引
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.83,0:44:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若能將那些無可取代的回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.44,0:44:14.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好珍惜並活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.38,0:44:23.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也別無所求
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.82,0:44:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盛開在那片天空下的夏之花
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.93,0:44:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨風緩緩飄落
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.10,0:44:44.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星光落在早已看不見的夜空
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.78,0:44:55.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那段日子將是我此生無可比喻的珍愛
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.00,0:45:07.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何憎恨
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.37,0:45:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何懊悔
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.67,0:45:12.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為何如此不可饒恕
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.44,0:45:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若真要捫心自問此意為何
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.58,0:45:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便如投身至無盡海底
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.01,0:45:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也如航行在無邊無際的大海
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.45,0:45:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為絕不可見
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.45,0:45:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也絕不可想之事
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.92,0:45:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茫茫冥海
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.12,0:45:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,縱使置身其中
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.03,0:45:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也絕不可窺探此境
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.36,0:45:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(海坊主)
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.16,0:46:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍色的月光照着你徘徊的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.97,0:46:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想說的話卻說不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.87,0:46:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日子令人如此不耐
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.84,0:46:25.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猶記那虛偽的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.28,0:46:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘卻那溫暖的淚水
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.78,0:46:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那雙失了魂的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.55,0:46:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,映照着什麼樣的風景？
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.49,0:46:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虛幻的下弦月隱臟在雲間
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.23,0:46:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗如今正慢慢浮現
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.33,0:46:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,述說着真相
Dialogue: 0,0:46:48.27,0:46:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擁抱着孤獨
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.07,0:46:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚是否又將對月長嘆…
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.08,0:47:01.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(大結局)
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.49,0:47:16.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,源慧師父五十年前
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.50,0:47:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您把令妹送進這裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.23,0:47:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓她一直漂流在這片大海是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.10,0:47:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然龍三角\N是由這艘船的怨念
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.17,0:47:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所衍生出來的妖怪之海啊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.11,0:47:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…\N那並非物怪的“真”啊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.95,0:47:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然這樣就打開獨木舟
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.79,0:47:43.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好祭拜裡面的死者
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.46,0:47:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就能讓船回到岸邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.06,0:47:48.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您…您是說要打開它？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.26,0:47:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太可怕了我辦不到
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.10,0:47:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是她被關在裡面五十年了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.87,0:47:59.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定…很想出來吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.74,0:48:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我會怕！
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.44,0:48:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太可怕了！
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.67,0:48:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人怎麼可能在這裡面\N活這麼久呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.01,0:48:08.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算她死了\N在海上漂流了五十年
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.11,0:48:11.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那屍體應該也腐爛了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.12,0:48:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因如此才更該超渡\N源慧師父之妹那可憐的靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.22,0:48:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是佛門子弟應盡的責任吧
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.99,0:48:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的非打開不可嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.20,0:48:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打開它…應該沒關係吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:48:30.04,0:48:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不想繼續在海上漂流
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.94,0:48:34.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到變成物怪的話
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.74,0:48:38.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該沒有人想變成物怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.65,0:48:42.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且賣藥的你來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.31,0:48:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是為了讓物怪上天成佛嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.99,0:48:55.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼準備打開吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.06,0:48:58.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一二！
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.30,0:49:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這卡得真緊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.97,0:49:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,賣藥的你別光在那看
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.94,0:49:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快過來幫忙啊！\N好再試一次
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.84,0:49:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一二…
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.98,0:49:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.25,0:49:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一二…
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.52,0:49:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.89,0:49:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家快逃呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.56,0:49:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的~
Dialogue: 0,0:49:26.69,0:49:29.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼老是這樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.38,0:49:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打開了耶！
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.10,0:50:16.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟阿庸出生在這片海域\N附近的某座小島上
Dialogue: 0,0:50:19.34,0:50:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父母很早就在海上遇難
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.35,0:50:25.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟阿庸相差五歲
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.08,0:50:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有其他同齡的玩伴
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.79,0:50:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此我們一直相依為命
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.53,0:50:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的感情真的很好
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.36,0:50:40.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不甚至可說是形影不離
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.23,0:50:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我十五歲時皈依佛門
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.47,0:50:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是島上的規定
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.68,0:50:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟阿庸都無法抵抗
Dialogue: 0,0:51:01.55,0:51:02.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.39,0:51:05.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿庸…
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.06,0:51:07.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令妹…
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.53,0:51:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人影跟形體…
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.36,0:51:11.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有遺骸都不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.13,0:51:17.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那時起
Dialogue: 0,0:51:17.40,0:51:19.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我改名為源慧
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.54,0:51:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離開小島\N過着嚴酷的修行生活
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.91,0:51:31.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,許多人熬不過辛苦的修行\N紛紛放棄離開
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.35,0:51:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而我努力熬了過去
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.32,0:51:37.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼做或許是想忘了阿庸吧\N源慧師父…
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.02,0:51:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是阿庸並沒有忘記我\N好多金魚到處都是金魚
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.86,0:51:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還一直祈禱\N我能成為了不起的僧侶
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.40,0:51:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了！有這麼多…
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.63,0:51:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在修行的那段期間\N只要有這些金魚哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.54,0:51:55.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我終於了解到…
Dialogue: 0,0:51:56.07,0:51:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄妹是…
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.98,0:52:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法結合的孽緣
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.81,0:52:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿庸的確是在這裡面啊…\N令妹似乎…
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.52,0:52:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是物怪喲~
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.59,0:52:16.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那物怪的“真”究竟是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.03,0:52:22.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又在測量跟物怪的距離？
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.67,0:52:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次不僅是測量距離
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.97,0:52:31.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還要將之引出來
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.28,0:52:34.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠請您告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.48,0:52:39.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,物怪的“真”嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.49,0:52:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於五十年前這艘獨木舟
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.22,0:52:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及令妹的事
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.66,0:52:48.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用天秤把物怪的“真”…
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.76,0:52:55.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找出來？
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.61,0:53:05.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好幾次我背離佛道及人道
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.44,0:53:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢見自已跟阿庸在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.65,0:53:15.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我還是選擇繼續修行
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.16,0:53:18.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後來呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.09,0:53:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能是為了積德吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:53:22.99,0:53:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是為了斬斷煩惱\N鍛鍊自我意志
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.70,0:53:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本該如此不是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.27,0:53:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很害怕…真的很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.21,0:53:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算無法結合\N我仍想待在阿庸身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.61,0:53:44.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才是我的真心
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.48,0:53:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:53:48.65,0:53:50.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿庸畢竟是個女人
Dialogue: 0,0:53:50.62,0:53:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遲早都得嫁作人婦
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.02,0:53:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是必須面對的現實
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.16,0:53:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我不願去面對
Dialogue: 0,0:53:59.06,0:54:01.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我害怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.57,0:54:04.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕自已在面對那個時刻
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.24,0:54:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將會成為面目可憎之人
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.51,0:54:15.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,源慧師父居然有過這種想法
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.88,0:54:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是有過
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.18,0:54:23.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是這個念頭\N一直都存於我心啊菖源
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.89,0:54:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是個六根不淨的師父\N抱歉！
Dialogue: 0,0:54:31.86,0:54:36.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是為什麼\N阿庸會坐進獨木舟呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.74,0:54:44.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.68,0:54:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.91,0:54:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開始修行的第五年
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.49,0:54:56.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在龍三角成為妖怪之海前
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.66,0:54:59.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就常常有船在此遇難
Dialogue: 0,0:55:00.23,0:55:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤其是那年夏天
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.50,0:55:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,島上有大半的船都沉沒了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.24,0:55:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接獲來自島上的信\N得知這件事的我
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.31,0:55:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把這件事當成自已的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.15,0:55:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信中雖沒明寫\N希望我成為鎮海的人柱
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.75,0:55:30.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(註：人柱為犧牲自我\N以平息眾神之怒之人)
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.62,0:55:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我心裡已有那樣的念頭
Dialogue: 0,0:55:37.40,0:55:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與其終其一生
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.56,0:55:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須一直害怕逃避\N自已那無法克制的心
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.20,0:55:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒不如成為鎮海之柱
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.64,0:55:47.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,島上的居民也是如此期盼
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.07,0:55:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此一來我也能就此解脫…
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.38,0:55:55.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是島民們順從了我的心願
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.71,0:55:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傾全力造了這艘獨木舟
Dialogue: 0,0:55:59.35,0:56:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獨木舟…\N這就是獨木舟出現的原因啊
Dialogue: 0,0:56:03.59,0:56:08.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是原本應該是\N源慧師父進入獨木舟的
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.59,0:56:11.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼變成阿庸小姐呢
Dialogue: 0,0:56:21.47,0:56:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,島民們完成了\N一艘非常美麗的獨木舟
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.15,0:56:29.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是這艘獨木舟
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.12,0:56:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛完成時它極盡華麗
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.06,0:56:38.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在準備出海的黎明
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.06,0:56:41.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我與阿庸重逢了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.59,0:56:46.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿庸已經成為16歲的美麗少女
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.53,0:56:50.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許我們不該見面的
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.40,0:56:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不管怎麼說突然
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.40,0:56:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我發現自已無法坐進獨木舟中
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.48,0:57:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…我害怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.95,0:57:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一想到要搭乘那艘獨木舟成佛
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.62,0:57:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我發現自已…根本辦不到
Dialogue: 0,0:57:15.73,0:57:18.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這時候阿庸溫柔地
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.40,0:57:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對那麼窩囊丟臉的我說了些話
Dialogue: 0,0:57:22.90,0:57:26.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她明明知道這樣的我
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.24,0:57:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就沒資格接受那些話
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.01,0:57:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但出航的時間就快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.35,0:57:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,島民們都希望我成為鎮海之柱
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.12,0:57:44.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此時阿庸說了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.66,0:57:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我代替哥哥搭乘獨木舟吧
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.00,0:57:56.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然我怎樣都不肯答應
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.84,0:58:00.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經過一番爭論後
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.81,0:58:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿庸又說
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.64,0:58:07.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然無法跟哥哥結合
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.48,0:58:10.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少讓我代替哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:58:10.88,0:58:13.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到佛祖的身邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.85,0:58:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哥哥修行的那段期間
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.22,0:58:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我每天都夢見哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.49,0:58:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能讓哥哥從痛苦中解脫
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.93,0:58:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我願意搭上獨木舟
Dialogue: 0,0:58:28.77,0:58:30.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼有這種事？
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.20,0:58:36.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來阿庸的想法跟我一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.21,0:58:41.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然無法白頭偕老
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.71,0:58:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如兩人一起搭上獨木舟
Dialogue: 0,0:58:46.15,0:58:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我連那種事都害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:58:49.89,0:58:54.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只想逃離現場
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.96,0:58:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我不斷對阿庸說
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.16,0:59:00.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會馬上自我了斷
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.50,0:59:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們來生再見
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.24,0:59:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我連尋死的勇氣都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.91,0:59:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是我選擇盡棄塵緣\N前往富士山
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.24,0:59:14.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天過着修行的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:59:17.35,0:59:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人們對我嚴苛的修行生活\N感到敬佩
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.19,0:59:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這五十年來
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.79,0:59:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我只是一直在為阿庸誦經
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.63,0:59:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以阿庸小姐坐上這獨木舟
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.60,0:59:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在海上漂流了五十年
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.17,0:59:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後卻成了物怪啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:59:41.24,0:59:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿庸小姐太可憐了！
Dialogue: 0,0:59:45.24,0:59:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.31,0:59:48.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？你說不對是什麼意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.71,0:59:51.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這片海上的物怪
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.15,0:59:56.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是阿庸小姐的怨念
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.99,0:59:59.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.66,1:00:02.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是“真”
Dialogue: 0,1:00:04.63,1:00:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來源慧師父
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.03,1:00:09.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您臟在手裡的東西…
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.97,1:00:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.64,1:00:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您一直看着這片海洋\N您在說什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.38,1:00:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為害怕阿庸小姐\N源慧師父的右眼…
Dialogue: 0,1:00:26.72,1:00:28.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕自已的心
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.62,1:00:31.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐懼不停縈繞着
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.69,1:00:33.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後變成連自已…
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.73,1:00:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都無法駕馭的黑影
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.06,1:00:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在海上徘徊巡視\N源慧師父！
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.47,1:00:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的“真”
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.43,1:00:44.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你！
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.47,1:00:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是這樣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.21,1:00:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來這五十年來
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.51,1:00:52.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直害怕這件事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:00:54.88,1:00:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那阿庸…阿庸到底在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,1:00:58.95,1:01:00.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿庸並沒變成物怪
Dialogue: 0,1:01:01.02,1:01:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她早已成為鎮海之柱
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.42,1:01:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與這片海洋合而為一
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.49,1:01:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個海座頭
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.02,1:01:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是您為了掩飾內心的恐懼
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.43,1:01:11.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而產生的
Dialogue: 0,1:01:17.70,1:01:19.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,分身
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.44,1:01:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,源慧師父！
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.48,1:01:29.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斬除物怪即斬除您的邪念
Dialogue: 0,1:01:29.75,1:01:35.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將兩顆分開的心合而為一
Dialogue: 0,1:01:35.15,1:01:39.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓您回歸最初的樣貌
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.39,1:01:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣您接受嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:01:41.96,1:01:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答！
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.23,1:01:50.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥…就讓我…\N我一定要飛黃騰達
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.34,1:01:54.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代替哥哥搭上獨木舟吧！\N當和尚也可以過好日子
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.07,1:01:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是為了死呢
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.84,1:01:57.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎？真的太遺憾了！
Dialogue: 0,1:01:58.08,1:02:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得救了這傢伙是白痴嗎？
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.58,1:02:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在到佛祖身邊之前\N我有一事相求
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.82,1:02:04.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事？該不會是要錢吧！
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.12,1:02:05.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可沒錢！
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.98,1:02:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從很久以前就…
Dialogue: 0,1:02:08.75,1:02:10.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直愛慕着哥哥
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.73,1:02:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.46,1:02:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然我無法跟哥哥結合
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.23,1:02:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少讓我代替哥哥
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.67,1:02:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到佛祖的身邊吧！
Dialogue: 0,1:02:28.11,1:02:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…真是太不可思議了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.91,1:02:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得自已不枉此生呢
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.09,1:02:44.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿庸的話讓我幡然醒悟
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.59,1:02:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老實說
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.93,1:02:51.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道自已是否喜歡阿庸
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.46,1:02:55.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是像我這無用之人
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.77,1:02:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也終於明白一件事
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.44,1:03:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是被愛的喜悅
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.31,1:03:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到花了這麼久的時間才懂啊
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.03,1:03:24.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩您
Dialogue: 0,1:03:25.83,1:03:27.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斬除我吧！
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.63,1:03:29.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解！
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.17,1:03:31.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解放！
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.31,1:03:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解…放！
Dialogue: 0,1:04:47.68,1:04:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,源慧師父…
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.98,1:04:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他沒事的還有呼吸呢
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.75,1:04:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他原來的長相真漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,1:04:57.22,1:05:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼…好像在笑呢
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.67,1:05:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.55,1:05:22.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿庸？
Dialogue: 0,1:05:26.18,1:05:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當你不在身邊
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.72,1:05:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就無法笑得開懷
Dialogue: 0,1:05:34.56,1:05:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這平凡的街道上
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.06,1:05:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是如此地被你吸引
Dialogue: 0,1:05:44.50,1:05:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若能將那些無可取代的回憶
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.24,1:05:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好珍惜並活下去
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.15,1:06:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也別無所求
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.49,1:06:14.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盛開在那片天空下的夏之花
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.57,1:06:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨風緩緩飄落
Dialogue: 0,1:06:20.91,1:06:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星光落在早已看不見的夜空
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.38,1:06:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那段日子將是我此生無可比喻的珍愛
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.24,1:06:54.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以來謝謝你了
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.15,1:07:05.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,1:07:05.85,1:07:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的眼睛…
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.40,1:07:27.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對…不能忘記哦！
Dialogue: 0,1:07:28.64,1:07:34.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(完)
